From 42dedea8e75161157d9d7c65dfaa229724d99ede Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Francesco Pham <francesco.pham1@h-partners.com>
Date: Tue, 14 Apr 2026 18:28:58 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] hybris: relax docs dir perms from 0711 to 0755

The sandboxed ExternalFileManager (FileAccess extension, uid 20010039)
needs the read bit on /mnt/user/<userId>/{no,}sharefs/docs and their
currentUser subdirs to enumerate them for the system file picker. With
mode 0711 it can traverse via the x bit but readdir returns EACCES, so
the picker UI shows an empty Internal Storage.

On stock OHOS the privileged file-access flow papers over this; on the
hybris_generic LXC build (no sharefs kernel driver, no per-URI filter)
the enumeration has to work at the directory-permission level. 0755
makes the dirs world-readable which matches the existing security
posture of this target and unblocks the file picker + every app that
consumes picker-returned URIs.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Change-Id: I956f7b95ae5672e012dd6e1da8441bcf7e17c5f1
---
 services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json | 8 ++++----
 1 file changed, 4 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json b/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
index 520b96eb..023e57ba 100644
--- a/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
+++ b/services/storage_daemon/storage_user_path.json
@@ -664,13 +664,13 @@
         },
         {
             "path": "/mnt/user/<userId>/nosharefs/docs",
-            "mode": "0711",
+            "mode": "0755",
             "uid": 0,
             "gid": 0
         },
         {
             "path": "/mnt/user/<userId>/nosharefs/docs/currentUser",
-            "mode": "0711",
+            "mode": "0755",
             "uid": 0,
             "gid": 0
         },
@@ -736,13 +736,13 @@
         },
         {
             "path": "/mnt/user/<userId>/sharefs/docs",
-            "mode": "0711",
+            "mode": "0755",
             "uid": 0,
             "gid": 0
         },
         {
             "path": "/mnt/user/<userId>/sharefs/docs/currentUser",
-            "mode": "0711",
+            "mode": "0755",
             "uid": 0,
             "gid": 0
         },
